detaileddescription.para: The resource consumption objectives for the component are defined in the SWA.

Performance: The performance objectives are defined in the SWA - see EA path: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ApplicationLayer.ZV_Lib.SW Architecture. Memory Consumption: The memory consumption objectives are defined in the SWA - see the following EA link: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ApplicationLayer.ZV_Lib.SW Architecture. CPU Load: The CPU load is represented in percent (Core0, Core1, Core2) and is defined in the SWA - see EA path: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ApplicationLayer.ZV_Lib.SW Architecture.
